Package: zzpower
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Power Analysis Calculator for Clinical Trial Designs
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: An interactive 'Shiny' application for power analysis and sample
    size calculations across multiple statistical tests. Supports two-group,
    paired, and one-sample t-tests, two-proportion comparisons, and correlation
    tests via a scalable plugin/registry architecture. Provides multiple effect
    size specifications per test, interactive power curves, detailed results
    tables, and downloadable reports. Designed for clinical researchers and
    statisticians planning studies.
